            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">AI Researcher, Data Scientist, and Technological Innovator
            </h1>
            <Prose>
              <div class="text-lg">
                <p>I'm Kayode Makinde, an AI researcher and data scientist dedicated to building technological solutions for real-world problems in Africa. 
                  My work spans across machine learning, computer vision, and reinforcement learning, with a focus on AI applications in agriculture, language translation, and beyond.
                  
                  <p>
                    I’ve been recognized for my academic achievements, AI innovations, and community leadership, and I’m committed to advancing AI adoption across industries in Nigeria and Africa.
                  </p>
                 
                </p>
