            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>Perizer – Data and Research Scientist</strong>
                    <br>
                    Remote | July 2024 – Present
                    <p>Lead AI and data-driven projects to improve predictive analytics and business intelligence for clients. Collaborate with teams on AI model integration.</p>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                    <strong>Perizer – Data and Research Scientist (Intern)</strong>
                    <br>
