            </ul>
        </section>

          <section>
          
            <h2>Achievements & Awards</h2>
            
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <strong>DataFest Africa Datathon Runner-Up</strong> (2024)
                    <p>Secured 2nd place and a 1M cash prize for developing an AI-driven solution to enhance student performance in Computer-Based Tests like JAMB and WASSCE.</p>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                    <strong>3rd Best Poster Award, IndabaX Nigeria</strong> (2024)
                    <p>Awarded 3rd Best Poster for the AI Plays Ayo project, showcasing AI's potential in cultural preservation and strategic gameplay.</p>
                </li>
            
                <li>
                    <strong>Mr. Algorithm, DSN AI Bootcamp</strong> (2024)
